345
00:17:13,652 --> 00:17:15,686
Activation de la sequence d'auto-destruction.

346
00:17:15,687 --> 00:17:18,289
Code 1-1-A-2-B.

347
00:17:18,290 --> 00:17:20,958
"sequence d'auto-destruction
